{"tid":178424,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度可以印一本書？","createTime":"2017-03-29T14:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T06:30:29.000Z","uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce545270ba0f2027e68d4a1f795fe316c1130ac","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"我想自己自己設計一本筆記簿<br />\n<br />\n所以想知邊度可以印到一本書<br />\n<br />\n但係上網見到嘅都係最少要印100本"},{"pid":"65781c44a443722b258bd63a303be482a54be57b","tid":178424,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:04:10.000Z","msg":"一本，我諗一係大廠，一係手工<br />\n你個設計有無咩特別？"},{"pid":"9d1bad247e527e32edee08b602a44ba7a2decc8c","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一本，我諗一係大廠，一係手工<br />\n你個設計有無咩特別？</blockquote><br />\n 點為之特別？"},{"pid":"01a814770c958243893c592cbd3232748d4e282b","tid":178424,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"做PROJECT果D釘裝?"},{"pid":"6bee8f12e3ef95c4121d8627d33a87573087fd5b","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做PROJECT果D釘裝?</blockquote><br />\n唔係釘裝<br />\n要線裝或者硬膠封面嘅"},{"pid":"f802b68b20a131b512257083de37e111072b162e","tid":178424,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"點會無，問下啲設計系學生去邊整作品集"},{"pid":"4852c7c18804f446e31d200fd6177cf11bfbbb77","tid":178424,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一本，我諗一係大廠，一係手工<br />\n你個設計有無咩特別？</blockquote><br />\n 點為之特別？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最普通係四色印落普通紙再釘裝<br />\n<br />\n特別係比較另類，例如燙金，螢光，有die cut 壓紋等甚至加配件例如金屬邊，膠片插卡位等等<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講，如果你唔係太熟印刷搵比較大嘅廠印會穩陣啲"},{"pid":"f8bc75770c6e5a0b75ef0073067f915f5206513e","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一本，我諗一係大廠，一係手工<br />\n你個設計有無咩特別？</blockquote><br />\n 點為之特別？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最普通係四色印落普通紙再釘裝<br />\n<br />\n特別係比較另類，例如燙金，螢光，有die cut 壓紋等甚至加配件例如金屬邊，膠片插卡位等等<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講，如果你唔係太熟印刷搵比較大嘅廠印會穩陣啲</blockquote><br />\n你講嗰啲我全部都冇嘅<br />\n咁知唔知邊到可以印一本？"},{"pid":"fc69a67aa6f8810f787abf25c128290cb35f6a84","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會無，問下啲設計系學生去邊整作品集</blockquote><br />\n呢度有冇設計系學生？"},{"pid":"792e311fbb590453b9c385ce44a4911abeb52b00","tid":178424,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"快圖美 吧啦"},{"pid":"008fe21a257ba5e5b4c8187570e24166db7c6a66","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快圖美 吧啦</blockquote><br />\n快圖美有得印？<br />\n我要指定嘅紙用嚟寫嘢喎"},{"pid":"3bc1f6d922c5bd5d92022609786e62f161b63362","tid":178424,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"之前去台灣有間店係教人自製notebook<br />\n可以參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://joyce8.com/bq2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoyce8.com%2Fbq2%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2dde937d\" target=\"_blank\">https://joyce8.com/bq2/</a>"},{"pid":"d78f7db7b7f57328de849a1b9b14f30840251a47","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去台灣有間店係教人自製notebook<br />\n可以參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://joyce8.com/bq2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoyce8.com%2Fbq2%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2dde937d\" target=\"_blank\">https://joyce8.com/bq2/</a></blockquote><br />\n我冇咁好技術"},{"pid":"86962204ffd440325c45850861a1fb76320d4c5f","tid":178424,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017